<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <!-- bootstrap -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

  <title>Gift Connect Homepage</title>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('templates/header') %>

    <div class="container-fluid">
      <p class="text-center">Have you ever been worried that you'll forget to buy a gift for someone? Clear your head by
        putting those thoughts on your Gift List Connect. One of the most important reasons you should use a to do list,
        even for gift buying, is that it will help you stay organized. When you write all your tasks in a list, they
        become more manageable. </p>
      <br>
      <p class="text-center">What is a Gift List Connect? The definition is a simple one. It's a list of gifts you need
        to purchase, or gifts that you want receive (under developement).</p>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>

    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
          aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="1"
          aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="2"
          aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-bs-slide-to="3"
          aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img src="https://unsplash.com/photos/PxM8aeJbzvk" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549465220-1a8b9238cd48?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NXx8Z2lmdHN8ZW58MHx8MHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60"
            class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607469256872-48074e807b0a?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Nnx8Z2lmdHN8ZW58MHx8MHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60"
            class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item">
          <img src="https://unsplash.com/photos/_qN6tmGjmtg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
        data-bs-slide="prev">
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleIndicators"
        data-bs-slide="next">
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <%- include('templates/footer'); %>

</body>

</html>